Class RBNBSourceObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • helpers.RBNBSourceObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RBNBSourceObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A custom class representation of an RBNB source object It contains the source name and type (e.g. log, metric, experiment) as well as a String list of all channels associated with that source
    Author:
    jdk85
